                            <comment id="17800" author="luke" created="Wed, 31 May 2006 05:13:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Note that the use of empty passwords is now disabled by default (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-284&quot; title=&quot;LdapAuthenticationProvider should always reject invalid usernames (problem with empty passwords)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SEC-284&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SEC-284&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for the reasons why). An empty password will result in a BadCredentialsException.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
